_sText:
This is a HUGE aim map created around a 7300GS graphics card that I was planning on selling on Ebay until I decided to make a map of it.
 
When I first started this map, I never thought it would become anything more than a prop for CS:S, but once I added in a spawn, I saw that it was alot bigger than I expected, so I built on that, and after 20 hours of mapping I bring to you, This!

This map was made entirely by me, also 95% of the textures are mine, with the other 5% being HL2 textures!

I have done the very long .nav generating for you so this map is ready for bot enabled servers!!


I realize that there are some texture issues, and I plan on fixing that when I have the time.  

Rest assured that I will be removing my massive logo on the roof of the map. Once I can take a better picture with my camera that is!
